Introduction

Choi Tae Hun is a South Korean singer and dancer under P Nation. He is a member of the boy group TNX. He was first known for appearing in the SBS survival show "Loud" where he was recruited to be a member of the boy group TNX. He made his official debut with the group on May 17, 2022.
